- Stop!

56:03.440 --> 56:07.080
- Judah, help me!
- (Guard) No!

56:07.160 --> 56:10.040
- (Simeon) No! No! No!
- (Guard) Let's go.

56:10.120 --> 56:12.080
(Door slams)

56:16.760 --> 56:19.720
Joseph, what are you doing?

56:19.800 --> 56:22.080
They're only feeding their families.

56:22.160 --> 56:25.880
They're thieves,
here to steal our grain.

56:25.960 --> 56:28.320
They needed food and they would pay.

56:28.400 --> 56:32.240
How can you say they're thieves?
They've done nothing to you.

56:32.320 --> 56:33.360
(Scoffs)

56:34.560 --> 56:36.640
Nothing?

56:38.320 --> 56:40.120
(Sighs)

56:41.240 --> 56:44.400
- They're my brothers.
- What?

56:44.480 --> 56:49.800
They sold me.
They sold me into slavery.

56:49.880 --> 56:52.320
They took me away from my home.

56:52.400 --> 56:55.120
I never got
to say goodbye to my mother.

56:55.200 --> 56:58.560
I never got
to see my father grow old.

57:01.000 --> 57:04.960
Joseph, I... I didn't know.

57:05.040 --> 57:09.600
You're here now. You have a home,
a wife who loves you,

57:09.680 --> 57:12.240
everything you could want.

57:12.320 --> 57:14.840
No. Not everything.

57:18.720 --> 57:21.920
I thought you learned something
in that cell.

57:22.800 --> 57:25.600
Remember when
I would bring food to you?

57:25.680 --> 57:29.440
Yes. It kept me going.

57:36.880 --> 57:39.840
(Simeon) Hey! You won't keep me here.

57:39.920 --> 57:42.080
My brothers will come for me.

57:42.160 --> 57:44.600
(Echoing) My brothers will come...

57:46.920 --> 57:48.320
